import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Typography,
  Paper,
  Link,
} from '@mui/material';

const Teaching: React.FC = () => {
  return (
    <Box>
      <Typography variant="h3" component="h1" gutterBottom>
        Teaching Experience
      </Typography>

      {/* Teaching Experience List */}
      <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 3 }}>
        {/* Current Course */}
        <Paper elevation={0} sx={{ p: 3, bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}>

            <Box sx={{ flex: { xs: '1 1 100%', md: '1 1 30%' } }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" color="primary">
                Fall 2023
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ flex: { xs: '1 1 100%', md: '1 1 70%' } }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                Course Title
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
                University Name
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                [Course description and your role]
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 2 }}>
                <Link href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  Course Website
                </Link>
                <Link href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  Syllabus
                </Link>
                <Link href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  Materials
                </Link>
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Paper>

        {/* Previous Course */}
        <Paper elevation={0} sx={{ p: 3, bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}>
          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: { xs: 'column', md: 'row' }, gap: 2 }}>
            <Box sx={{ flex: { xs: '1 1 100%', md: '1 1 30%' } }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" color="primary">
                Spring 2023
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ flex: { xs: '1 1 100%', md: '1 1 70%' } }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                Course Title
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
                University Name
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                [Course description and your role]
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 2 }}>
                <Link href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  Course Website
                </Link>
                <Link href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  Syllabus
                </Link>
                <Link href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  Materials
                </Link>
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Paper>

        {/* Earlier Course */}
        <Paper elevation={0} sx={{ p: 3, bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}>
          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: { xs: 'column', md: 'row' }, gap: 2 }}>
            <Box sx={{ flex: { xs: '1 1 100%', md: '1 1 30%' } }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" color="primary">
                Fall 2022
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ flex: { xs: '1 1 100%', md: '1 1 70%' } }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                Course Title
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
                University Name
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                [Course description and your role]
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 2 }}>
                <Link href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  Course Website
                </Link>
                <Link href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  Syllabus
                </Link>
                <Link href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  Materials
                </Link>
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Paper>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Teaching;
